wow these last few days have prolly been the worst of my life.  i didnt end up going to see evanescence like i planed on doing.  thursday my grandma had to go to the hospital.  they dont kno what is wrong with her.  she is gettin better now tho so thats good.  also thursday my sweet tart decided he was going to join the navy.  he had to stay at a hotel that night to take the physical the next day and sign up.  he did all that and went to sign up and they didnt have the job he wanted.  so he was sposed to go monday for another job but went on vacation with his family.  that means no sweet tart for a week =-(  i dunno what he plans on doing when he comes back.  i hope he doesnt sign up.  i want him to be happy but i dunno.  i dont think he needs that. he could do good on his own.  i will miss him sooooooooo much if he goes.  i miss him already and he has only been on his vacation for a day.  heh

i still want to go see evanescence so if anybody wants to go.  i need to get tickets soon

anywho...i got a new bedroom set for my room.  im almost done putting it togehter and gettin everything put in its new spot.  today was the last monday i ever have to go to school.  i went for 1st block and a tiny part of 3rd then i had to go to the doctors. =-( i dont like going to the doctors.  all the roads were flooded so i had to go around everything.  after that i was hungry so me and my blue sweet tart went to the buffet. mmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmm pizza buffet!!  i went back to school for the end part of 7th block.  then i had track.  after that i came home and just messed around in my room trying to put everything together.  im real tired so i think ima just go to sleep now! 

~night all!~

first off, i didnt "run away".  i had to leave otherwise me and my mom would have killed each other.  i am home now.  i would appriciate it if people didnt spread my business around either.  whoever reads this i think are my freinds.  but to open your mouths and tell everybody and their brother, thanks i appriciate it.  

in other news...i would like to thank everyone  that took care of me while i was homeless for 48 hours lol. taurean aka blue sweet tart gets the most appriciation, even tho he is the one that got me in trouble in the first place!!! u were right, u did take care of me. prolly only because you buy me papmpers, you buy me milk, you love me. hahahahahahhaha def seeing jerry in the summer! =-) when are we going to see shreck 2?!?!??! forrest-thanks for not lettin ur dog eat me! and eating cheese fries! mmmmmmmmmm good times, good times.  

regionals are tomorrow.  that means school on senior skip day.  so very lame!  oh well.  hopefully i do ok.

got a new bedroom set.  i have to put that together this weekend. 

evanescence is coming july 15th i think. anybody want to go with me? its at pine knob and lawn tickets are like $25.  i really want to go but i need someone to go with me!!
its funny how your life can change so fast.  this is my last day at home.  i have a track meet at 4 so after that im not comming home.  its so scary. i dunno what im going to do with myself.

im excited.  i finally get to sleep tonight.  i havent really slept since sun night/mon morning...wtf  blue sweet tart is at work so i get to sleep! lol

prom was a blast!! i had so much fun.  everyone looked so nice =-) had a lot of fun after too.  heffalump!! haha i dunno what i can say about her and after prom but "this is triple black, your only half black" hahahhahahahahhahahahaha hhahhahahhahahahahhahahahahahhahahahhahahahahhahahahhahahahaha
def one of the most funniest things ive ever heard in my life! hahahahahahaha

we had a track meet the next day....bah!  i must have only slept 30-45 mins at the most.  i kept falling asleep!  that night me and taurean watched jerry.  that show is the shit! "he buy me pampers and milk....he love me!!" hahahahhaha so funny.  

monday and tuesday i pulled all nighters.  someone keeps me up at night...no jelly beans tho, those are out like whoa.  sweet tarts are the in thing now. lol

wednesday i went to the tigers game with eric.  it was fun.  we say laura and steve there so it was sweet.  talked on the phone for awhile.  fell asleep while i was talking lol

today i had to work after practice.  i got the rest of my pictures developed.  they are sweet.  prom was so fun.  i loved my dress so i keep looking at my pics!

next week is going to go by fast! sunday is the senior athletic banquet.  that will be fun.  monday is this honers cermony or something.  i dunno what im gettin.  i guess ill find out soon! tues and wed we have no school.  tuesday is our last reg season track meet too.  i want to throw at least 90 feet.  i think i can do it.  so far ive placed at every meet and i plan on gettin first for our last one, just like i did the first one! lol  thurs and fri are senior skip days.  i cant skip fri cuz that is the day for regionals so i have to go to school.  it will be sweet tho cuz i wont have to do anything but sit there.  i plan to nap that day.  

june 5th is coming faster and faster.  i cant wait to get my cap and gown cuz then ill really feel like im bout to graduate.  im so excited!  june 19 is my grad party.  if u would like to attend let me kno or comment or something.  we need to kno how much food to have!

i want to go to another tigers game and sit in the pepsi bleachers and get free food.  that would be the shit!  shreck 2 comes out next fri! im so excited! i cant wait to see it.  i love shreck!

2 and a half months till linkin park!! im cant wait for that.  def will be the shit!

ps. anybody want to go to wapred tour with me?  its in august

wow i havent wrote in here in a long time.  spring break was real fun.  i miss the bahamas, it was good times.  my mom keeps teasing me cuz she thinks shes going to hear about me on girls gone wild or something.  now where would she get that idea that im not a good kid!?

track season has been fun so far.  its fun haning out after school with people since i only have to go for another month or so.  

i FINALLY went to the zoo! it was fun.  taurean aka t-bone took me.  we got in for free and didnt pay for parking either. i dont think that was sposed to happen....but oh well.  i <3 the penguins. =-)  ima steal one and take it home one day! i had a lot of fun that day.

graduation is soon.  i dunno what im going to do with myself. school?  air force?  bum?   any suggestions?

prom is this friday.  im kinda excited.  i will that day, but now its very stressful.  i have to get my dress pressed, hair done, nails done, that flower thing that boys wear, go tanning to blend my skin from peeling after the bahamas. i dunno what im going to do after.  i think eric wont be able to stay all night but for a while.  so after he leaves i dunno whats going to happen.  its going to be sweet taking a hummer limo there tho!

i cant wait till summer.  ill be working more and have more money!  hopefully ill be able to do stuff and go places and not be a poor bum!  speaking of being a poor bum, i owe my mom money and need to go to the bank to pay her.  i hate owing other people money.  i like to pay to get it outta the way.  i bought a dvd player the other day.  its pretty sweet.  im like up with the times now.  

well im out cuz taurean is on the phone and wants me to go with him to get his tounge pierced. lol

march went by fast.  since track started i feel so busy all the time.  i go to school at 7:15, track till 4:30ish, work till 7ish, socialize till like 10:30ish then i just go to bed.  

SPRING BREAK!!!!!!!!!! yea it sucks i leave on easter sunday but oh well.  so ill be in the bahamas from April 11-18! im so excited! i cant wait! the casino better watch out for me!  itll be good to get away from it all.  

prom is soon too! may 7.  i got my dress and shoes.  im so excited to wear them! i cant wait for prom. its going to be a good night. 

GRADUATION!!!! JUNE 5, 10AM!  35 school days left and counting......

tomorrow im going to this wedding deal with my mom.  eric is going with us.  i have to pick lil peg up from the airport tomorrow to.  so we have to leave right after we eat then we might go back, i dunno, whatever.  

i dont really have anything else to write about.  i dont really do much anymore but school, track, work, sleep.  cant wait till school is out!

well, i dunno when i last wrote in hurr.  im finally 18 now.  its so great.  i went to the bar for the first time, it was really fun.  i got the tattoo i wanted finally! i love it.  its sweet as hell.  its almost spring break! thank god! im so excited.  itll be nice and warm there! =-) im going to see linkin park july 26.  graduation is june 5.  prom is may 7.  i need to go look for a dress! things are going good, life is gettin better.  im very happy.

my birthday is march 9 and im going to eat at mongolian bbq, so if u would like to join let me kno!:-)

wow.  friday after school i went to the bank, to brittanis house, to the mall, to get my nails done, and to the bball game.  right before the bball game i noticed that my thorat hurt.  so when i came home i went pretty much right to bed.  sat i get up and went into my moms room cuz thats how shitty i felt.  she took me to the drs.  it turns out that i have not only a sinus infection, but strept thorat also.  great.  i could barely even swallow.  its a lil bit better now, but im not better.  blah i hate being sick.  so therefore, im missing ANOTHER day of school, and ANOTHER gold day. heh good to be a senior i guess.  well this senior is going to lay down now

this last week has been nuts. i work like everyday, and even tho its only like 3 hours or w/e, i dont like it cuz i like to come home from school and take a nap cuz ima lazy bum.  

Valentines day came and went.  i thought it was going to be a sad day but it wasnt.  it was very nice.  eric took me out to eat then to the movies.  i had lots of fun.  aww he brought me a rose too, and a lil stuffed animal.  it was cute.   i had a very lovely evening. 

today i had a gay soccer game at 11:30.  it was really the worst game ive ever played in my entire life.  eric came to watch and i felt like and idiot cuz i sucked so bad. we only had like 1 sub tho. oh well, maybe next time.  today at work we were short a girl.  on top of doing all of her work, the dishwasher broke.  heh great.  we still got outta there at 7 tho so it wasnt too bad.

my birthday is in 23 days.  everyone better start gettin my presents now. =-)

so today is my first day off since sunday.  tuesday i went into work late cuz i had to go to the doctors about being kicked in the face at soccer.  they thought my sinuses were dislodged. oh man crazy stuff there.  yesterday after work ryan came over.  after he left i talked to eric for awhile.  we talked till i couldnt keep my eyes open anymore and had to go to bed, which is like 12:30. lol

today after school i picked up both of my checks and cashed in my bonds and went to the bank cuz my bahama trip money came. and i thought i would have to take money out, well it ended up i got to put money in.  woop woop im + and not -! go meeeeeee! after that me and my mom went to mongoluan bbq! mmmmmmmmm and guess who was eating at the table next to us...thats right! HB at 6!! omg boner in my pants! yea, how exciting! 

i have to work friday, saturday, and sunday...how lame

hopefully eveything will work out and me and eric will be able to hang out saturday as planned.  at least i wont have to be all alone on valentines day.
